164
00:12:46,966 --> 00:12:48,991
See you later.

165
00:12:53,272 --> 00:12:56,241
I must help him to recover.

166
00:12:56,442 --> 00:12:58,911
In order to look after him,

167
00:12:58,911 --> 00:13:01,277
