Stop complaining, Suzanna.

190
00:15:26,125 --> 00:15:28,218
Yes, I know.

191
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,362
Right, starts.

192
00:15:43,542 --> 00:15:46,578
People who never get hurt,

193
