233
00:19:06,044 --> 00:19:08,274
I must pass this test.

234
00:19:08,514 --> 00:19:10,415
For Mr.Albert.

235
00:19:10,415 --> 00:19:15,318
I hope I could accept
Terry's invitation as a real nurse.

236
00:19:16,989 --> 00:19:19,287
Why are you here?

237
